::'''Seymour:''' Fret not. I've discussed this with the other members of the Hex Club. Our "Hexanexus: Remake" will soon be accessible on the Skysplitter platform as a cross-platform game! It's set to be a completely revamped version, promising gamers an entirely fresh experience.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You people truly have connections everywhere.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401550411-->
:::'''Seymour:''' Unless you're not keen to play, there's simply no reason you can't play it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'd rather have a clean Skysplitter.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401550412-->
:::'''Seymour:''' Our Hexanexus are sterilized and treated with anti-virus, so please do not worry.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_401550415-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401550415-->
